&gt;聽日14:50考油塘，希望呢個post保佑保佑 一take pass,依家去補第二次鐘二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n油塘多車 記住cut線時果條線清空哂先好cut&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n師傅都話，泊好車cut 兩條線都最好cut兩次，穩陣啲</blockquote><br />\n邊個畀你連cut兩線 根本唔得 cut完一條你唔熄定仲想cut 得你自己知 好多當你未熄就唔畀位 加上左右後鏡望唔到咁開"},{"pid":"5bd38c6fa7ca5645ee29c220875f525d43829181","tid":8220,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功泊左位，之後出街就未驚過<br />\n利申：忠義街一take pass</blockquote><br />\n忠義唔係路試後泊咩"},{"pid":"6d769b776c8ed0161b5be14bfba2072963aeb450","tid":8220,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醒定d <br />\n<br />\n唔係下個到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/005609_4a1bdcd94124b34c06fa126fb76bf622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F005609_4a1bdcd94124b34c06fa126fb76bf622.jpg&h=4088de21&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主你黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔離post個絲打？"},{"pid":"97950eec1f0edcc45cae90631e3f8ae90a44eb9b","tid":8220,"uid":4315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:09:00.000Z","msg":"震倒仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af65c7e8e5ced6827d1cacafa8950c10e51238b","tid":8220,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"手都震埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉錯波"},{"pid":"909a1e09500f4456fa0857f47ac5d6cfcae70502","tid":8220,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出發考車，11點永孝街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永考街加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0427b47bde0b17e041006de31a9ae132f3dac310","tid":8220,"uid":5339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:10:24.000Z","msg":"我就考 <br />\n最驚到時震到仆街 衰左泊車<br />\n跟住冇晒信心衰埋路試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38ea65d32511aa5bc442e8343fa8f1cee0d6dda","tid":8220,"uid":37129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今朝考 腳都軟 之前想申請延期個師父叫看考埋佢話有危險考牌官會幫我渣返返黎 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點知琴日就撞左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fdf4ca74fab0a4065400d63e809e08a100e7d0","tid":8220,"uid":20151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"泊車1take pass<br />\n路試停車唔記得空波 直接2波開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe6b3b8ff07571e3365555add90d475b57a955d","tid":8220,"uid":26784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我考果時震到吊唔到極力子 之後同個考官講「可唔可以俾少少時間我冷靜下 我驚到腳震」<br />\n諗返起都覺得自己膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee91a03501aae9e3dc5d39aab7977d319bbee85d","tid":8220,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出發考車，11點永孝街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永考街加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1月6 永孝街<br />\n宜家都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae477a5e46f5cd1dc5e4c285bf4871fefe664e61","tid":8220,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出發考車，11點永孝街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永考街加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1月6 永孝街<br />\n宜家都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考完，1 take pass。<br />\n一開頭泊位冇緊張，正常發揮。<br />\n一到調頭開始緊張腳震。<br />\n完成左乙部出路面調整好心情就正常發揮，<br />\n最危險係永基路三線轉右，我行中線，拖頭右線，<br />\n我一早已經有意識要讓佢轉先，燈位時仲特登望下佢個尾架長度，不過拖頭真係太慢，畀人tick 左太接近其他物體。"},{"pid":"c6a2fbaa9991636447a1d1efc68cc076cecda924","tid":8220,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:10:13.000Z","msg":"有個月小心得畀啲吊極力子吊得唔好既巴打，<br />\n可以試下著啲好薄底既鞋，容易D feel 到個腳踏震同踩左幾多。<br />\n我有一堂試過著red wing 學車，即刻柒吓柒吓，吊唔到極力子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3095f73c0af47ab62d596d7fa098395187aba98","tid":8220,"uid":6935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"岩岩考完油塘，pass左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到試場時見到架考試車撞左sosad"},{"pid":"24ecaa20cecd9bae90360d7cceff5cec3faf64fc","tid":8220,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出發考車，11點永孝街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永考街加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1月6 永孝街<br />\n宜家都好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考完，1 take pass。<br />\n一開頭泊位冇緊張，正常發揮。<br />\n一到調頭開始緊張腳震。<br />\n完成左乙部出路面調整好心情就正常發揮，<br />\n最危險係永基路三線轉右，我行中線，拖頭右線，<br />\n我一早已經有意識要讓佢轉先，燈位時仲特登望下佢個尾架長度，不過拖頭真係太慢，畀人tick 左太接近其他物體。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泊位同調頭緊張好多，可能一錯位就肥所以勁慢勁小心"},{"pid":"de7a4790320e881ba777f3fbf1f877821f7c5931","tid":8220,"uid":49758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"記得當年考泊位震到控制唔到隻左腳結果泊位上博肥乙部，丙部就唔知點解合格左"},{"pid":"a73c55cb8f25213bf51ea3ac589acc53f9ffb134","tid":8220,"uid":4150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人都震，我又係震到不得了，連考牌官都望我隻腳，好彩狂剔之下都pass，大家腳震都唔駛怕，照揸得架啦"},{"pid":"4a928bc25a0a04306b74e195afa93070208c5394","tid":8220,"uid":416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"由頭震到落尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223a70980f27cace6260f232b0a9f64b9ca33c49","tid":8220,"uid":16201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"輕鬆1 take pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過考完個官唔出聲好撚cool咁走真係驚到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd07549de7ba5252f99789c6e1054f2f0010a7ad","tid":8220,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕鬆1 take pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過考完個官唔出聲好撚cool咁走真係驚到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌呢啲官又真係仆街 真係以為自己係官好撚大官威咩 你係咁勁就唔使仲坐喺架車度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b9a981c4c5e03f24ba647e86f496ae50e546e5","tid":8220,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T19:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個月小心得畀啲吊極力子吊得唔好既巴打，<br />\n可以試下著啲好薄底既鞋，容易D feel 到個腳踏震同踩左幾多。<br />\n我有一堂試過著red wing 學車，即刻柒吓柒吓，吊唔到極力子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我著timberland 去學同去考<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係太關事"},{"pid":"6d662b57f979f1a713164770064e5daffa5efd1c","tid":8220,"uid":14570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T22:02:16.000Z","msg":"泊位果陣左腳震到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後 1 take pass 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c54bcdf999671868cd34a4efc60807e18f617c","tid":8220,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泊位果陣左腳震到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後 1 take pass 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係左腳震"},{"pid":"ae2675cc2e8d1c2ff24efb738303ede581422ff1","tid":8220,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:07:29.000Z","msg":"有無咁撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">驚到考之前個晚訓唔著</span>"},{"pid":"c6af0bb4d83993bddb1bd7723e09434fd587d589","tid":8220,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:24:31.000Z","msg":"考輕型果陣無震，反而考中型嗰陣震到仆街，因為公司老細1take pass，問題係佢手車屎，所以好撚大壓力<br />\n<br />\n泊位攞得唔夠前，好彩技術搭救，車尾一到即停，連回軚時間都無，啱啱入咗格仔，因為壓力大再加埋咁驚險，做三手調頭嗰陣隻腳震到仆街，一路吊住極力子一路大幅度un腳，但奇就奇在架車好定又唔會chok，我都唔知自己點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f731fcb4554aeb456605dcc243f0f2f6c1c5d60","tid":8220,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"考輕型果陣無震，反而考中型嗰陣震到仆街，因為公司老細1take pass，問題係佢手車屎，所以好撚大壓力<br />\n<br />\n泊位攞得唔夠前